## Why earth tones

The Sanskrit word आखाड़ा refers to a wrestling/practice arena — a literal earthen ground. The palette evokes that: sienna and saddle-brown for the arena floor, chocolate for the pit walls, wheat for the warm lamp-light over the practice mat. The voice-roleplay product is about disciplined preparation, not flashy gamification — earth tones convey grounded seriousness.

